|--------|------|-------|
| **Modify** | `server/package.json` | Add `"type": "module"`, `better-sqlite3` dep, test/dev/start scripts |
| **Modify** | `kanban/package.json` | Add `"test:db": "npm -w server run test"` to scripts |
